data.description: Another money-making opportunity in the City of Atlanta comes easy with this property.  Three bedrooms, living room, kitchen, dining area and 2 bathrooms on a basement provides the space and basics for a beautiful renovation.  The interior has original hardwood floors.  The roof is 6 years old.  The HVAC is 4 years old.  Located in Hot Venetian Hills with renovations throughout the neighborhood, this property is less than 2.5 miles to the Atlanta Beltline.  Nearby are exciting new developments including Lee & White, Murphy Crossing and Tyler Perry Studios
